<h1>CloudCall</h1>
<img src="img/CloudCall.png" class="img-responsive right" alt="CloudCall by Synety" />
<p>CloudCall turns your Act! instance into a one-stop-shop for sales and support communications.The solution can be quickly activated within Act! allowing users to take advantage of key features such as click-to- call, call recording and real-time performance analytics.</p>
<p>Inbound and outbound calls are routed directly through Act!, allowing representatives to never have to leave the system. Reps can stay in the system they already know and are working in, maximizing their time with prospects and customers.</p>
<ul>
	<li><strong>Search Call History:</strong> Search and monitor calls the same as you would with email</li>
  <li><strong>Save Recordings on Contact Records:</strong> Store sales and support call recordings in Act! alongside other activities and communications</li>
  <li><strong>Call Recording:</strong> Replay recorded conversations for training or problem resolution</li>
  <li><strong>Easy Install:</strong> Quickly and easily integrates with your existing Act! architecture</li>
  <li><strong>Call Reporting and Analytics:</strong> In-depth reporting on call activity by sales rep, including call duration and number of calls made</li>
  <li><strong>Compliance:</strong> Pause and restart call recordings mid-call for privacy and compliance requirements</li>
  <li><strong>Inbound Screen Popping:</strong> Receive pop up alert containing the contact’s record on inbound calls</li>
</ul>

